data.name: lblInfo.Text
data.value:
Hello, I'm your B2S screen resolution identifier. Please let me help you setup your B2S settings.
I have opened three windows for you. These three windows are dummy windows for the playfield, the backglass and the DMD screen. Use these three windows, drag and drop them whereever you want to have them. But maybe the easiest way is to choose your type of setup at first so you get a recommendation for your setup from me.
So, first of all you have to choose between a 1-, 2- or 3-screen setup. I have found {0} screen(s) on your system, so it's up to you now: - in a 1-screen setup everything happens on the primary screen. - in a 2-screen setup the playfield has to be on the primary screen, the second screen is used for the backglass AND the DMD. The backglass is WITH grill and the DMD is matching the grill. - in a 3-screen setup the playfield has to be on the primary screen, another screen is for the backglass WITHOUT grill and a third screen is for the DMD.
